data.description: Nestled on a serene wooded corner lot, this brick gem harmoniously merges nature's beauty with modern living. From the living area, the vast window reveals a lush tree-scape and distinct boulder backdrop. An updated HVAC ensures year-round comfort. The home's inherent charm is ripe for personal touches, making it not just a house but a potential haven. Ideally situated in a coveted neighborhood, you're minutes from shopping, fine dining, and top schools. Whether you wish to tweak or transform, this home awaits your touch. A canvas of potential and scenic allure, it's the home you've envisioned.
